何体的形态特点，我们可以将其分为以下几类：</p>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;1.               &emsp;<strong>柱体</strong>：有两个平行且大小相同的多边形底面，侧面为平行四边形的几何体。特殊柱体包括：             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"0\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">正方体</span></strong               >：六个面都是正方形的特殊长方体，所有棱长相等。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 180px; margin: 0 50px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/square.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 120%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"1\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">长方体</span></strong               >：六个面都是矩形的平行六面体，且相对的两个面完全相同。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/cuboid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"2\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆柱</span></strong               >：底面为圆，侧面为曲面的几何体，母线与底面垂直。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/cylinder.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;2. &emsp;               <strong>锥体</strong               >：有一个顶点，其余各点都在一个平面上（底面），且侧面都是三角形的几何体。特殊锥体包括：             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1）&emsp;               <strong><span data-id=\"3\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆锥</span></strong               >：底面为圆，顶点在底面圆心上方的几何体，侧面为曲面，母线与底面圆相交于一点。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/triangular.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"4\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">棱锥</span></strong               >：底面为多边形，顶点不在底面上的几何体，侧面为三角形。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/quadrangular.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             &emsp;&emsp;3. &emsp;             <strong><span data-id=\"5\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球体</span></strong             >：所有点都与球心等距的点的集合，表面为曲面，无棱无顶点。             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/6.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/circle.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <br /><br />             <h4>&emsp;&emsp;几何体的基本性质与特征</h4>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp;<strong>面</strong>：几何体由若干个面组成，面可以是平面也可以是曲面。             </p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp;<strong>棱</strong>：两个相邻面的交线称为棱，棱是直线段。</p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;<strong>顶点</strong>：三条或三条以上棱的交点称为顶点。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;4.&emsp;<strong>底面</strong>：在几何体中，处于最下方的平面部分称为底面（对于锥体而言）。             </p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;5.&emsp;<strong>侧面</strong>：除底面外的其他面称为侧面。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;6.&emsp;<strong>高</strong>：从底面某一点垂直到底面另一侧（或顶点）的最短距离称为高。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;7.&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"6\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">母线</span                 >（仅适用于圆锥、圆柱等）</strong               >：连接顶点与底面圆周上任意一点的线段。             </p>             <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">               <img src=\"/content/course1/7.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 400px\" />             </p>             <br />             <h4>&emsp;&emsp; 特征总结：</h4>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp; 正方体和长方体具有规则的棱长和面形，易于计算和描述。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp;               圆柱和圆锥的底面为圆，侧面为曲面，其表面积和体积计算涉及圆周率和积分概念。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;               棱柱和棱锥的底面为多边形，侧面为三角形或矩形，其性质与底面形状密切相关。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;4.&emsp; 球体作为唯一没有棱和顶点的几何体，其所有点都等距于<strong                 ><span data-id=\"7\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球心</span></strong               >，具有完美的对称性。             </p>             <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; margin: 20px 0\">               <img src=\"/content/course1/8.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 240px\" />               <img src=\"/content/course1/9.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 220px\" />             </p>           </div>', 1823340924497637376);
INSERT INTO `knowledge` VALUES (0, ' <div>             <h4>&emsp;&emsp;定义：</h4>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;立体几何是研究三维空间中物体的形状、大小、位置关系的数学分支。立体几何体，简称几何体，是由平面图形围绕某一直线或平面旋转，或平移而得到的具有一定体积和形状的物体。             </p>             <br />             <h4>&emsp;&emsp;分类：</h4>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;根据几何体的形态特点，我们可以将其分为以下几类：</p>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;1.               &emsp;<strong>柱体</strong>：有两个平行且大小相同的多边形底面，侧面为平行四边形的几何体。特殊柱体包括：             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"0\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">正方体</span></strong               >：六个面都是正方形的特殊长方体，所有棱长相等。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 180px; margin: 0 50px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/square.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 120%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"1\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">长方体</span></strong               >：六个面都是矩形的平行六面体，且相对的两个面完全相同。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/cuboid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"2\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆柱</span></strong               >：底面为圆，侧面为曲面的几何体，母线与底面垂直。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/cylinder.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;2. &emsp;               <strong>锥体</strong               >：有一个顶点，其余各点都在一个平面上（底面），且侧面都是三角形的几何体。特殊锥体包括：             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1）&emsp;               <strong><span data-id=\"3\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆锥</span></strong               >：底面为圆，顶点在底面圆心上方的几何体，侧面为曲面，母线与底面圆相交于一点。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/triangular.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"4\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">棱锥</span></strong               >：底面为多边形，顶点不在底面上的几何体，侧面为三角形。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/quadrangular.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             &emsp;&emsp;3. &emsp;             <strong><span data-id=\"5\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球体</span></strong             >：所有点都与球心等距的点的集合，表面为曲面，无棱无顶点。             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/6.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/circle.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <br /><br />             <h4>&emsp;&emsp;几何体的基本性质与特征</h4>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp;<strong>面</strong>：几何体由若干个面组成，面可以是平面也可以是曲面。             </p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp;<strong>棱</strong>：两个相邻面的交线称为棱，棱是直线段。</p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;<strong>顶点</strong>：三条或三条以上棱的交点称为顶点。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;4.&emsp;<strong>底面</strong>：在几何体中，处于最下方的平面部分称为底面（对于锥体而言）。             </p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;5.&emsp;<strong>侧面</strong>：除底面外的其他面称为侧面。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;6.&emsp;<strong>高</strong>：从底面某一点垂直到底面另一侧（或顶点）的最短距离称为高。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;7.&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"6\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">母线</span                 >（仅适用于圆锥、圆柱等）</strong               >：连接顶点与底面圆周上任意一点的线段。             </p>             <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">               <img src=\"/content/course1/7.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 400px\" />             </p>             <br />             <h4>&emsp;&emsp; 特征总结：</h4>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp; 正方体和长方体具有规则的棱长和面形，易于计算和描述。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp;               圆柱和圆锥的底面为圆，侧面为曲面，其表面积和体积计算涉及圆周率和积分概念。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;               棱柱和棱锥的底面为多边形，侧面为三角形或矩形，其性质与底面形状密切相关。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;4.&emsp; 球体作为唯一没有棱和顶点的几何体，其所有点都等距于<strong                 ><span data-id=\"7\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球心</span></strong               >，具有完美的对称性。             </p>             <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; margin: 20px 0\">               <img src=\"/content/course1/8.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 240px\" />               <img src=\"/content/course1/9.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 220px\" />             </p>           </div>', ' <div>             <h4>&emsp;&emsp;定义：</h4>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;立体几何是研究三维空间中物体的形状、大小、位置关系的数学分支。立体几何体，简称几何体，是由平面图形围绕某一直线或平面旋转，或平移而得到的具有一定体积和形状的物体。             </p>             <br />             <h4>&emsp;&emsp;分类：</h4>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;根据几何体的形态特点，我们可以将其分为以下几类：</p>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;1.               &emsp;<strong>柱体</strong>：有两个平行且大小相同的多边形底面，侧面为平行四边形的几何体。特殊柱体包括：             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"0\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">正方体</span></strong               >：六个面都是正方形的特殊长方体，所有棱长相等。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 180px; margin: 0 50px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/square.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 120%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"1\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">长方体</span></strong               >：六个面都是矩形的平行六面体，且相对的两个面完全相同。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/cuboid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"2\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆柱</span></strong               >：底面为圆，侧面为曲面的几何体，母线与底面垂直。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/cylinder.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;2. &emsp;               <strong>锥体</strong               >：有一个顶点，其余各点都在一个平面上（底面），且侧面都是三角形的几何体。特殊锥体包括：             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1）&emsp;               <strong><span data-id=\"3\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆锥</span></strong               >：底面为圆，顶点在底面圆心上方的几何体，侧面为曲面，母线与底面圆相交于一点。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/triangular.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"4\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">棱锥</span></strong               >：底面为多边形，顶点不在底面上的几何体，侧面为三角形。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/quadrangular.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             &emsp;&emsp;3. &emsp;             <strong><span data-id=\"5\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球体</span></strong             >：所有点都与球心等距的点的集合，表面为曲面，无棱无顶点。             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/6.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/circle.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <br /><br />             <h4>&emsp;&emsp;几何体的基本性质与特征</h4>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp;<strong>面</strong>：几何体由若干个面组成，面可以是平面也可以是曲面。             </p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp;<strong>棱</strong>：两个相邻面的交线称为棱，棱是直线段。</p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;<strong>顶点</strong>：三条或三条以上棱的交点称为顶点。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;4.&emsp;<strong>底面</strong>：在几何体中，处于最下方的平面部分称为底面（对于锥体而言）。             </p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;5.&emsp;<strong>侧面</strong>：除底面外的其他面称为侧面。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;6.&emsp;<strong>高</strong>：从底面某一点垂直到底面另一侧（或顶点）的最短距离称为高。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;7.&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"6\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">母线</span                 >（仅适用于圆锥、圆柱等）</strong               >：连接顶点与底面圆周上任意一点的线段。             </p>             <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">               <img src=\"/content/course1/7.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 400px\" />             </p>             <br />             <h4>&emsp;&emsp; 特征总结：</h4>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp; 正方体和长方体具有规则的棱长和面形，易于计算和描述。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp;               圆柱和圆锥的底面为圆，侧面为曲面，其表面积和体积计算涉及圆周率和积分概念。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;               棱柱和棱锥的底面为多边形，侧面为三角形或矩形，其性质与底面形状密切相关。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;4.&emsp; 球体作为唯一没有棱和顶点的几何体，其所有点都等距于<strong                 ><span data-id=\"7\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球心</span></strong               >，具有完美的对称性。             </p>             <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; margin: 20px 0\">               <img src=\"/content/course1/8.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 240px\" />               <img src=\"/content/course1/9.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 220px\" />             </p>           </div>', 1823594959465164800);
INSERT INTO `knowledge` VALUES (0, ' <div>             <h4>&emsp;&emsp;定义：</h4>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;立体几何是研究三维空间中物体的形状、大小、位置关系的数学分支。立体几何体，简称几何体，是由平面图形围绕某一直线或平面旋转，或平移而得到的具有一定体积和形状的物体。             </p>             <br />             <h4>&emsp;&emsp;分类：</h4>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;根据几何体的形态特点，我们可以将其分为以下几类：</p>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;1.               &emsp;<strong>柱体</strong>：有两个平行且大小相同的多边形底面，侧面为平行四边形的几何体。特殊柱体包括：             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"0\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">正方体</span></strong               >：六个面都是正方形的特殊长方体，所有棱长相等。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 180px; margin: 0 50px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/square.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 120%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"1\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">长方体</span></strong               >：六个面都是矩形的平行六面体，且相对的两个面完全相同。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/cuboid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"2\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆柱</span></strong               >：底面为圆，侧面为曲面的几何体，母线与底面垂直。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/cylinder.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;2. &emsp;               <strong>锥体</strong               >：有一个顶点，其余各点都在一个平面上（底面），且侧面都是三角形的几何体。特殊锥体包括：             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1）&emsp;               <strong><span data-id=\"3\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆锥</span></strong               >：底面为圆，顶点在底面圆心上方的几何体，侧面为曲面，母线与底面圆相交于一点。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/triangular.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"4\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">棱锥</span></strong               >：底面为多边形，顶点不在底面上的几何体，侧面为三角形。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/quadrangular.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             &emsp;&emsp;3. &emsp;             <strong><span data-id=\"5\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球体</span></strong             >：所有点都与球心等距的点的集合，表面为曲面，无棱无顶点。             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/6.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/circle.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <br /><br />             <h4>&emsp;&emsp;几何体的基本性质与特征</h4>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp;<strong>面</strong>：几何体由若干个面组成，面可以是平面也可以是曲面。             </p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp;<strong>棱</strong>：两个相邻面的交线称为棱，棱是直线段。</p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;<strong>顶点</strong>：三条或三条以上棱的交点称为顶点。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;4.&emsp;<strong>底面</strong>：在几何体中，处于最下方的平面部分称为底面（对于锥体而言）。             </p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;5.&emsp;<strong>侧面</strong>：除底面外的其他面称为侧面。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;6.&emsp;<strong>高</strong>：从底面某一点垂直到底面另一侧（或顶点）的最短距离称为高。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;7.&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"6\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">母线</span                 >（仅适用于圆锥、圆柱等）</strong               >：连接顶点与底面圆周上任意一点的线段。             </p>             <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">               <img src=\"/content/course1/7.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 400px\" />             </p>             <br />             <h4>&emsp;&emsp; 特征总结：</h4>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp; 正方体和长方体具有规则的棱长和面形，易于计算和描述。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp;               圆柱和圆锥的底面为圆，侧面为曲面，其表面积和体积计算涉及圆周率和积分概念。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;               棱柱和棱锥的底面为多边形，侧面为三角形或矩形，其性质与底面形状密切相关。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;4.&emsp; 球体作为唯一没有棱和顶点的几何体，其所有点都等距于<strong                 ><span data-id=\"7\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球心</span></strong               >，具有完美的对称性。             </p>             <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; margin: 20px 0\">               <img src=\"/content/course1/8.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 240px\" />               <img src=\"/content/course1/9.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 220px\" />             </p>           </div>', ' <div>             <h4>&emsp;&emsp;定义：</h4>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;立体几何是研究三维空间中物体的形状、大小、位置关系的数学分支。立体几何体，简称几何体，是由平面图形围绕某一直线或平面旋转，或平移而得到的具有一定体积和形状的物体。             </p>             <br />             <h4>&emsp;&emsp;分类：</h4>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;根据几何体的形态特点，我们可以将其分为以下几类：</p>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;1.               &emsp;<strong>柱体</strong>：有两个平行且大小相同的多边形底面，侧面为平行四边形的几何体。特殊柱体包括：             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"0\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">正方体</span></strong               >：六个面都是正方形的特殊长方体，所有棱长相等。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 180px; margin: 0 50px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/square.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 120%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"1\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">长方体</span></strong               >：六个面都是矩形的平行六面体，且相对的两个面完全相同。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/cuboid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"2\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆柱</span></strong               >：底面为圆，侧面为曲面的几何体，母线与底面垂直。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/cylinder.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;2. &emsp;               <strong>锥体</strong               >：有一个顶点，其余各点都在一个平面上（底面），且侧面都是三角形的几何体。特殊锥体包括：             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1）&emsp;               <strong><span data-id=\"3\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆锥</span></strong               >：底面为圆，顶点在底面圆心上方的几何体，侧面为曲面，母线与底面圆相交于一点。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/triangular.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"4\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">棱锥</span></strong               >：底面为多边形，顶点不在底面上的几何体，侧面为三角形。             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/quadrangular.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             &emsp;&emsp;3. &emsp;             <strong><span data-id=\"5\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球体</span></strong             >：所有点都与球心等距的点的集合，表面为曲面，无棱无顶点。             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <img src=\"/content/course1/6.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course1/circle.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <br /><br />             <h4>&emsp;&emsp;几何体的基本性质与特征</h4>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp;<strong>面</strong>：几何体由若干个面组成，面可以是平面也可以是曲面。             </p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp;<strong>棱</strong>：两个相邻面的交线称为棱，棱是直线段。</p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;<strong>顶点</strong>：三条或三条以上棱的交点称为顶点。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;4.&emsp;<strong>底面</strong>：在几何体中，处于最下方的平面部分称为底面（对于锥体而言）。             </p>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;5.&emsp;<strong>侧面</strong>：除底面外的其他面称为侧面。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;6.&emsp;<strong>高</strong>：从底面某一点垂直到底面另一侧（或顶点）的最短距离称为高。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;7.&emsp;<strong                 ><span data-id=\"6\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">母线</span                 >（仅适用于圆锥、圆柱等）</strong               >：连接顶点与底面圆周上任意一点的线段。             </p>             <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">               <img src=\"/content/course1/7.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 400px\" />             </p>             <br />             <h4>&emsp;&emsp; 特征总结：</h4>             <p>&emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp; 正方体和长方体具有规则的棱长和面形，易于计算和描述。</p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp;               圆柱和圆锥的底面为圆，侧面为曲面，其表面积和体积计算涉及圆周率和积分概念。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;               棱柱和棱锥的底面为多边形，侧面为三角形或矩形，其性质与底面形状密切相关。             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;4.&emsp; 球体作为唯一没有棱和顶点的几何体，其所有点都等距于<strong                 ><span data-id=\"7\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球心</span></strong               >，具有完美的对称性。             </p>             <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; margin: 20px 0\">               <img src=\"/content/course1/8.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 240px\" />               <img src=\"/content/course1/9.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 220px\" />             </p>           </div>', 1824617623197065216);
INSERT INTO `knowledge` VALUES (1, '<div>             <h3>&emsp;&emsp;一、表面积的计算</h3>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp;<strong>定义：</strong>表面积（S）是立体图形外部所有面的面积之和。             </p>             <p>               <iframe                 src=\"/static/course2/c2-3to2.html\"                 frameborder=\"0\"                 scrolling=\"no\"                 style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"               ></iframe>             </p>             <br />             <p>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp;<strong>基本形状的表面积</strong></p>             <div>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"7\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">长方体：</span></strong               >设长、宽、高分别为 l,w,h，则表面积               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </p>               <!--              <span> \\[ S_{\\text{长方体}} = 2(lw + lh + wh) \\]</span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m1.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </div>             <div></div>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/cuboid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/square.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"8\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">正方体：</span> </strong               >（特殊长方体）：设边长为 a，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{正方体}} = 6a^2 \\]</span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m2.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/cube.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"9\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆柱体：</span></strong               >设底面半径为 r，高为 h，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 120px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆柱体}} = 2\\pi r^2 + 2\\pi rh \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m3.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/cylinder.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（4）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"10\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆锥体：</span></strong               >设底面半径为 r，斜边（母线）长为 l，则表面积 <br />               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（注意：这里假设圆锥侧面展开后为<span                 data-id=\"11\"                 style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\"                 >扇形</span               >，且其弧长等于底面圆的周长）             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆锥体}} = \\pi r^2 + \\pi rl \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m4.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/pyramid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（5）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"12\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆台：</span></strong               >设圆台的上底面半径为 r，下底面半径为 R（R>r），高为 h，斜边（母线）长为 l。则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆台}} = \\pi r^2 + \\pi R^2 + \\pi (r + R) l \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m5.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/round.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（6）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"13\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球体：</span></strong               >设半径为 r，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/6.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 170px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{球体}} = 4\\pi r^2 \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m6.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/circle.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;               <strong>组合体表面积计算：</strong               >对于由多个基本形状组合而成的立体，需分别计算各部分的表面积，并根据组合方式（如拼接、挖空等）进行加减调整，注意共享面在计算时只计算一次。             </p>             <br />             <h3>&emsp;&emsp;二、体积的计算</h3>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp; <strong>定义：</strong>体积（V）是立体图形所占空间的大小。             </p>             <br />             <p>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp; <strong>基本形状体积公式：</strong></p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1） <strong>长方体：</strong>设长、宽、高分别为               l,w,h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{长方体}} = lwh \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m7.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2） <strong>正方体：</strong>设底面半径为 r，高为               h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{正方体}} = a^3 \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m8.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3） <strong>圆柱体：</strong>（特殊长方体）：设边长为               a，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 120px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆柱体}} = \\pi r^2 h \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m9.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（4） <strong>圆锥体：</strong>设底面半径为 r，高为               h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆锥体}} = \\frac{1}{3}\\pi r^2 h \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m10.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（5） <strong>圆台体：</strong>设圆台的上底面半径为               r，下底面半径为 R（R>r），高为 h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />               </span> <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆台体}} = \\frac{1}{3} \\pi h (R^2 + r^2 + Rr) \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m11.png\" alt=\"\">               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（6） <strong>球体：</strong>设半径为 r，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/6.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 170px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{球体}} = \\frac{4}{3}\\pi r^3 \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m12.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;               <strong>组合体体积计算：</strong               >组合体的体积计算通常更为直接，只需将各部分的体积相加即可。若存在挖空部分，则需从总体积中减去相应体积。             </p>           </div>', '<div>             <h3>&emsp;&emsp;一、表面积的计算</h3>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp;<strong>定义：</strong>表面积（S）是立体图形外部所有面的面积之和。             </p>             <p>               <iframe                 src=\"/static/course2/c2-3to2.html\"                 frameborder=\"0\"                 scrolling=\"no\"                 style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"               ></iframe>             </p>             <br />             <p>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp;<strong>基本形状的表面积</strong></p>             <div>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"7\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">长方体：</span></strong               >设长、宽、高分别为 l,w,h，则表面积               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </p>               <!--              <span> \\[ S_{\\text{长方体}} = 2(lw + lh + wh) \\]</span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m1.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </div>             <div></div>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/cuboid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/square.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"8\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">正方体：</span> </strong               >（特殊长方体）：设边长为 a，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{正方体}} = 6a^2 \\]</span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m2.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/cube.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"9\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆柱体：</span></strong               >设底面半径为 r，高为 h，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 120px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆柱体}} = 2\\pi r^2 + 2\\pi rh \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m3.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/cylinder.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（4）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"10\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆锥体：</span></strong               >设底面半径为 r，斜边（母线）长为 l，则表面积 <br />               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（注意：这里假设圆锥侧面展开后为<span                 data-id=\"11\"                 style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\"                 >扇形</span               >，且其弧长等于底面圆的周长）             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆锥体}} = \\pi r^2 + \\pi rl \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m4.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/pyramid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（5）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"12\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆台：</span></strong               >设圆台的上底面半径为 r，下底面半径为 R（R>r），高为 h，斜边（母线）长为 l。则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆台}} = \\pi r^2 + \\pi R^2 + \\pi (r + R) l \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m5.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/round.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（6）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"13\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球体：</span></strong               >设半径为 r，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/6.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 170px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{球体}} = 4\\pi r^2 \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m6.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/circle.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;               <strong>组合体表面积计算：</strong               >对于由多个基本形状组合而成的立体，需分别计算各部分的表面积，并根据组合方式（如拼接、挖空等）进行加减调整，注意共享面在计算时只计算一次。             </p>             <br />             <h3>&emsp;&emsp;二、体积的计算</h3>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp; <strong>定义：</strong>体积（V）是立体图形所占空间的大小。             </p>             <br />             <p>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp; <strong>基本形状体积公式：</strong></p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1） <strong>长方体：</strong>设长、宽、高分别为               l,w,h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{长方体}} = lwh \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m7.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2） <strong>正方体：</strong>设底面半径为 r，高为               h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{正方体}} = a^3 \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m8.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3） <strong>圆柱体：</strong>（特殊长方体）：设边长为               a，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 120px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆柱体}} = \\pi r^2 h \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m9.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（4） <strong>圆锥体：</strong>设底面半径为 r，高为               h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆锥体}} = \\frac{1}{3}\\pi r^2 h \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m10.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（5） <strong>圆台体：</strong>设圆台的上底面半径为               r，下底面半径为 R（R>r），高为 h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />               </span> <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆台体}} = \\frac{1}{3} \\pi h (R^2 + r^2 + Rr) \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m11.png\" alt=\"\">               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（6） <strong>球体：</strong>设半径为 r，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/6.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 170px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{球体}} = \\frac{4}{3}\\pi r^3 \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m12.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;               <strong>组合体体积计算：</strong               >组合体的体积计算通常更为直接，只需将各部分的体积相加即可。若存在挖空部分，则需从总体积中减去相应体积。             </p>           </div>', 1822964565643108352);
INSERT INTO `knowledge` VALUES (1, '<div>             <h3>&emsp;&emsp;一、表面积的计算</h3>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp;<strong>定义：</strong>表面积（S）是立体图形外部所有面的面积之和。             </p>             <p>               <iframe                 src=\"/static/course2/c2-3to2.html\"                 frameborder=\"0\"                 scrolling=\"no\"                 style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"               ></iframe>             </p>             <br />             <p>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp;<strong>基本形状的表面积</strong></p>             <div>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"7\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">长方体：</span></strong               >设长、宽、高分别为 l,w,h，则表面积               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </p>               <!--              <span> \\[ S_{\\text{长方体}} = 2(lw + lh + wh) \\]</span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m1.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </div>             <div></div>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/cuboid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/square.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"8\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">正方体：</span> </strong               >（特殊长方体）：设边长为 a，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{正方体}} = 6a^2 \\]</span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m2.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/cube.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"9\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆柱体：</span></strong               >设底面半径为 r，高为 h，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 120px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆柱体}} = 2\\pi r^2 + 2\\pi rh \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m3.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/cylinder.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（4）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"10\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆锥体：</span></strong               >设底面半径为 r，斜边（母线）长为 l，则表面积 <br />               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（注意：这里假设圆锥侧面展开后为<span                 data-id=\"11\"                 style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\"                 >扇形</span               >，且其弧长等于底面圆的周长）             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆锥体}} = \\pi r^2 + \\pi rl \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m4.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/pyramid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（5）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"12\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆台：</span></strong               >设圆台的上底面半径为 r，下底面半径为 R（R>r），高为 h，斜边（母线）长为 l。则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆台}} = \\pi r^2 + \\pi R^2 + \\pi (r + R) l \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m5.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/round.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（6）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"13\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球体：</span></strong               >设半径为 r，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/6.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 170px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{球体}} = 4\\pi r^2 \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m6.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/circle.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;               <strong>组合体表面积计算：</strong               >对于由多个基本形状组合而成的立体，需分别计算各部分的表面积，并根据组合方式（如拼接、挖空等）进行加减调整，注意共享面在计算时只计算一次。             </p>             <br />             <h3>&emsp;&emsp;二、体积的计算</h3>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp; <strong>定义：</strong>体积（V）是立体图形所占空间的大小。             </p>             <br />             <p>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp; <strong>基本形状体积公式：</strong></p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1） <strong>长方体：</strong>设长、宽、高分别为               l,w,h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{长方体}} = lwh \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m7.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2） <strong>正方体：</strong>设底面半径为 r，高为               h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{正方体}} = a^3 \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m8.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3） <strong>圆柱体：</strong>（特殊长方体）：设边长为               a，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 120px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆柱体}} = \\pi r^2 h \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m9.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（4） <strong>圆锥体：</strong>设底面半径为 r，高为               h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆锥体}} = \\frac{1}{3}\\pi r^2 h \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m10.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（5） <strong>圆台体：</strong>设圆台的上底面半径为               r，下底面半径为 R（R>r），高为 h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />               </span> <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆台体}} = \\frac{1}{3} \\pi h (R^2 + r^2 + Rr) \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m11.png\" alt=\"\">               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（6） <strong>球体：</strong>设半径为 r，则体积            