div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"8\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">正方体：</span> </strong               >（特殊长方体）：设边长为 a，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{正方体}} = 6a^2 \\]</span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m2.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/cube.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"9\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆柱体：</span></strong               >设底面半径为 r，高为 h，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 120px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆柱体}} = 2\\pi r^2 + 2\\pi rh \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m3.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/cylinder.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（4）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"10\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆锥体：</span></strong               >设底面半径为 r，斜边（母线）长为 l，则表面积 <br />               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（注意：这里假设圆锥侧面展开后为<span                 data-id=\"11\"                 style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\"                 >扇形</span               >，且其弧长等于底面圆的周长）             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆锥体}} = \\pi r^2 + \\pi rl \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m4.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/pyramid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <br />