    <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆锥体}} = \\pi r^2 + \\pi rl \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m4.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/pyramid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（5）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"12\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆台：</span></strong               >设圆台的上底面半径为 r，下底面半径为 R（R>r），高为 h，斜边（母线）长为 l。则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆台}} = \\pi r^2 + \\pi R^2 + \\pi (r + R) l \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m5.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/round.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（6）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"13\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球体：</span></strong               >设半径为 r，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/6.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 170px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{球体}} = 4\\pi r^2 \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m6.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/circle.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;               <strong>组合体表面积计算：</strong               >对于由多个基本形状组合而成的立体，需分别计算各部分的表面积，并根据组合方式（如拼接、挖空等）进行加减调整，注意共享面在计算时只计算一次。             </p>             <br />             <h3>&emsp;&emsp;二、体积的计算</h3>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp; <strong>定义：</strong>体积（V）是立体图形所占空间的大小。             </p>             <br />             <p>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp; <strong>基本形状体积公式：</strong></p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1） <strong>长方体：</strong>设长、宽、高分别为               l,w,h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{长方体}} = lwh \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m7.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2） <strong>正方体：</strong>设底面半径为 r，高为               h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{正方体}} = a^3 \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m8.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3） <strong>圆柱体：</strong>（特殊长方体）：设边长为               a，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 120px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆柱体}} = \\pi r^2 h \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m9.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（4） <strong>圆锥体：</strong>设底面半径为 r，高为               h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆锥体}} = \\frac{1}{3}\\pi r^2 h \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m10.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（5） <strong>圆台体：</strong>设圆台的上底面半径为               r，下底面半径为 R（R>r），高为 h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />               </span> <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆台体}} = \\frac{1}{3} \\pi h (R^2 + r^2 + Rr) \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m11.png\" alt=\"\">               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（6） <strong>球体：</strong>设半径为 r，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/6.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 170px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{球体}} = \\frac{4}{3}\\pi r^3 \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m12.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;               <strong>组合体体积计算：</strong               >组合体的体积计算通常更为直接，只需将各部分的体积相加即可。若存在挖空部分，则需从总体积中减去相应体积。             </p>           </div>', 1823334531849859072);
INSERT INTO `knowledge` VALUES (1, '<div>             <h3>&emsp;&emsp;一、表面积的计算</h3>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp;<strong>定义：</strong>表面积（S）是立体图形外部所有面的面积之和。             </p>             <p>               <iframe                 src=\"/static/course2/c2-3to2.html\"                 frameborder=\"0\"                 scrolling=\"no\"                 style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"               ></iframe>             </p>             <br />             <p>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp;<strong>基本形状的表面积</strong></p>             <div>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"7\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">长方体：</span></strong               >设长、宽、高分别为 l,w,h，则表面积               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </p>               <!--              <span> \\[ S_{\\text{长方体}} = 2(lw + lh + wh) \\]</span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m1.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </div>             <div></div>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/cuboid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/square.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"8\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">正方体：</span> </strong               >（特殊长方体）：设边长为 a，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{正方体}} = 6a^2 \\]</span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m2.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/cube.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"9\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆柱体：</span></strong               >设底面半径为 r，高为 h，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 120px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆柱体}} = 2\\pi r^2 + 2\\pi rh \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m3.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/cylinder.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（4）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"10\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆锥体：</span></strong               >设底面半径为 r，斜边（母线）长为 l，则表面积 <br />               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（注意：这里假设圆锥侧面展开后为<span                 data-id=\"11\"                 style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\"                 >扇形</span               >，且其弧长等于底面圆的周长）             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆锥体}} = \\pi r^2 + \\pi rl \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m4.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/pyramid.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（5）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"12\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">圆台：</span></strong               >设圆台的上底面半径为 r，下底面半径为 R（R>r），高为 h，斜边（母线）长为 l。则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{圆台}} = \\pi r^2 + \\pi R^2 + \\pi (r + R) l \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m5.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/round.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>              <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（6）               <strong                 ><span data-id=\"13\" style=\"color: #63b0ff; cursor: pointer\">球体：</span></strong               >设半径为 r，则表面积             </p>             <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%\">               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/6.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 170px\" />                 </span>                 <!--                <span> \\[ S_{\\text{球体}} = 4\\pi r^2 \\] </span>-->                 <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                   <img src=\"/content/course2/m6.png\" alt=\"\" />                 </span>               </p>               <p style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 50%\">                 <iframe                   src=\"/static/course2/circle.html\"                   frameborder=\"0\"                   scrolling=\"no\"                   style=\"width: 100%; height: 50vh\"                 ></iframe>               </p>             </div>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;3.&emsp;               <strong>组合体表面积计算：</strong               >对于由多个基本形状组合而成的立体，需分别计算各部分的表面积，并根据组合方式（如拼接、挖空等）进行加减调整，注意共享面在计算时只计算一次。             </p>             <br />             <h3>&emsp;&emsp;二、体积的计算</h3>             <br />             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;1.&emsp; <strong>定义：</strong>体积（V）是立体图形所占空间的大小。             </p>             <br />             <p>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;2.&emsp; <strong>基本形状体积公式：</strong></p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（1） <strong>长方体：</strong>设长、宽、高分别为               l,w,h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{长方体}} = lwh \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m7.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（2） <strong>正方体：</strong>设底面半径为 r，高为               h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 200px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{正方体}} = a^3 \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m8.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（3） <strong>圆柱体：</strong>（特殊长方体）：设边长为               a，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 120px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆柱体}} = \\pi r^2 h \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m9.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（4） <strong>圆锥体：</strong>设底面半径为 r，高为               h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 160px\" />               </span>               <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆锥体}} = \\frac{1}{3}\\pi r^2 h \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m10.png\" alt=\"\" />               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（5） <strong>圆台体：</strong>设圆台的上底面半径为               r，下底面半径为 R（R>r），高为 h，则体积               <span style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 150px\" />               </span> <!--              <span> \\[ V_{\\text{圆台体}} = \\frac{1}{3} \\pi h (R^2 + r^2 + Rr) \\] </span>-->               <span style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center\">                 <img src=\"/content/course2/m11.png\" alt=\"\">               </span>             </p>             <p>               &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;（6） <strong>球体：</strong>设半径为 r，则体积            